Class FeatureFilterBase<T extends IFeature>

java.lang.Object
org.sensorhub.api.resource.ResourceFilter<T>
org.sensorhub.api.datastore.feature.FeatureFilterBase<T>
Type Parameters:
T - Type of resource supported by this filter
All Implemented Interfaces:
Predicate<T>, IQueryFilter
Direct Known Subclasses:
DeploymentFilter, FeatureFilter, FoiFilter, ProcedureFilter, SystemFilter
public abstract class FeatureFilterBase<T extends IFeature> extends ResourceFilter<T>

Base class for feature filters.
There is an implicit AND between all filter parameters.
